heading: Sanguine Chapel Dungeon Guide
content: Sanguine Chapel stores the which is OK for extra Rogue resource. However, the mediocre layout leaves much to be desired when running this dungeon over and over again for XP and loot. Look for other more optimal dungeons rather than this one. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
